name: Silver Child Graduation Cap, Gown & Tassel
description:
Silver Child Cap, Gown & Tassel
•Cap and gown crafted from sleek, non see through shiny finish
•Reinforced stitching throughout the gown
•Silver shiny tricot fabric
•Durable zipper in matching Silver color
•Classic center pleats in the front of the gown
•Package comes with a one size fits all cap
•Tassel included with commemorative year drop
